---
// The left half of this panel is intentionally empty: it is the resting place
// of the shared portrait that glides in from the hero (wired in Stage B).
---

<section class="section about" id="about" aria-label="About">
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="ab-body">
      <p class="ab-hook reveal reveal-x" style="--i:0">Shaped by business, technology, and media.</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-x" style="--i:1">
        I am interested in how digital products are structured, how they guide people, and how they
        create trust. For me, design is not only about the surface, but about clarity, usability, and
        the small decisions that make an experience feel effortless.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-x" style="--i:2">
        What fascinates me about UX is that good design often goes unnoticed. When it works, people
        simply understand where they are, what they can do, and what happens next. That is the kind of
        design I want to create: useful, trustworthy, and calm, but with enough character to feel distinct.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-x" style="--i:3">
        Outside of design, I am drawn to experiences that combine structure, atmosphere, and detail,
        whether in games, movies, or cooking. I like when many small decisions come together to create
        something people remember.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-foot">
    <div class="ab-footer">
      <div class="ab-foot-col reveal" style="--i:3">
        <p class="ab-foot-label">Education</p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line">M.Sc. Digital Media &mdash; <span class="ab-school">TH&nbsp;Brandenburg</span></p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line">B.Sc. Social Media Systems &mdash; <span class="ab-school">TH&nbsp;Mittelhessen</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-foot-col reveal" style="--i:4">
        <p class="ab-foot-label">Languages</p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line">German &mdash; native</p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line">English &mdash; C1</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-foot-col reveal" style="--i:5">
        <p class="ab-foot-label">Location</p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line">Berlin Metropolitan Area</p>
        <p class="ab-foot-line"><span class="soft">(open to relocate)</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    width: 100vw;
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .about-content {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50vw;
    right: 6vw;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-58%);
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .ab-body {
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* scoped under .ab-body so it beats the `.ab-body p` body style */
  .ab-body .ab-hook {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(21px, 1.9vw, 27px);
    line-height: 1.36;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .ab-body p {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    max-width: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 16.5px;
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: #d7d0c4;
  }

  .ab-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* footer strip pinned along the bottom, divided by thin rules */
  .about-foot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50vw;
    right: 6vw;
    bottom: 8.5vh;
    padding-top: 26px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .ab-footer {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.7fr 1fr 1.05fr;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .ab-school {
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ab-foot-col {
    padding-right: 22px;
  }

  .ab-foot-col + .ab-foot-col {
    padding-left: 22px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .ab-foot-label {
    margin: 0 0 13px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .ab-foot-line {
    margin: 0 0 5px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .ab-foot-line:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .ab-foot-line .soft {
    color: #6f6a64;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px), (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-content {
      position: static;
      left: auto;
      right: auto;
      transform: none;
      padding: 22vh 7vw 0;
    }

    .ab-body {
      max-width: none;
    }

    .about-foot {
      position: static;
      left: auto;
      right: auto;
      bottom: auto;
      margin: 40px 7vw 12vh;
    }

    .ab-footer {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 26px;
    }

    .ab-foot-col {
      padding-right: 0;
    }

    .ab-foot-col + .ab-foot-col {
      padding-top: 22px;
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
  }
</style>
